{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, techniques combining capture/replay seeding with LLMs have been proven to further improve the understandability of generated tests [33].",
    "These findings collectively demonstrate the significant potential of LLMs in enhancing test engineering quality.",
    "System-level Synergistic IntegrationThe techniques discussed above primarily focus on improving the generation quality of LLMs themselves.",
    "However, relying solely on LLMs remains challenging when dealing with complex path coverage or constraint solving tasks.",
    "This has prompted researchers to explore the system-level synergistic integration of LLMs with traditional tools adept at structured exploration (as shown in Table 6)."
  ]
}